Package xxl.core.relational.resultSets

Class Summary
AbstractResultSet This class is a skeleton for writing non-abstract classes that implement the result set interface.
DecoratorResultSet This class decorates a result set.
MetaDataCursorResultSet This class wraps a metadata cursor to a result set.
ResultSets This class contains various useful static methods for managing columns of result sets.
VirtualTable This class is a wrapper for result sets with the intention to receive an instance of the VTI (Virtual Table Interface) in order to use the wrapped result set in a FROM clause of an SQL-J statement.
